---
# Production Memory Manager Configuration
# Optimized settings for production use with teams and large projects

# Search Configuration
defaultSearchMode: both  # Use both semantic and text for best results

# Auto-Indexing Settings
autoIndex:
  enabled: true
  batch_size: 5  # Higher batch for efficiency
  min_content_length: 20
  max_content_length: 5000
  priority_important: true  # Prioritize important conversations

# Embedding Configuration
embedding:
  model: claude-sonnet-4-6
  dimensions: 1536
  index_conversations: true
  cache_results: true  # Cache embedding results

# Database Settings
database:
  path: ~/.claude/memory/memory.db
  max_size_mb: 1000  # Higher threshold for production
  backup_enabled: true
  backup_path: ~/.claude/memory/backups
  backup_retention_days: 30  # Keep backups for 30 days

# Retention Policy
retention:
  conversations_days: 365  # 1 year retention
  unindexed_days: 60  # Shorter for unindexed
  keep_tagged: true
  keep_critical: true  # Never delete important

# Cleanup Settings
cleanup:
  enabled: true
  schedule: weekly
  day: sunday
  prune_old: true
  rebuild_indexes: true
  optimize_storage: true
  analyze_plans: true  # Analyze query plans

# Indexing Triggers
indexingTriggers:
  session_end: true
  summary_update: true
  explicit_request: true
  periodic_scan: true  # Scan periodically for missed conversations

# Performance Settings
performance:
  async_operations: true
  max_concurrent_requests: 5  # Higher for production
  timeout_seconds: 45
  retry_attempts: 5  # More retries for resilience
  retry_delay_ms: 1000

# Logging
logging:
  enabled: true
  level: info
  path: ~/.claude/memory/memory.log
  rotation_enabled: true
  max_log_size_mb: 10
  retention_days: 30

# Team/Shared Settings
team:
  shared_memory: false  # Set true if sharing across team
  sync_enabled: false  # Enable for team sync
  conflict_resolution: timestamp  # How to resolve conflicts

# Search Optimization
search:
  enable_fts_search: true
  vector_distance_function: cosine
  min_relevance_score: 0.5  # Lower threshold for more results
  result_limit: 30
  include_full_context: false
  cache_queries: true

# Security
security:
  encrypt_database: false  # Enable encryption for sensitive data
  access_log_enabled: true
  audit_trail: true

# Monitoring
monitoring:
  health_check_enabled: true
  alert_on_error: true
  performance_tracking: true
  report_anomalies: true

# Advanced Settings
advanced:
  enable_fts_search: true
  vector_distance_function: cosine
  embedding_cache_enabled: true
  query_optimization: true
  result_ranking: hybrid  # Combine semantic and text relevance

---

# Production Configuration Guide

## Overview

This configuration is optimized for production environments with:
- Teams and multiple users
- Large conversation history
- Frequent usage
- Reliability requirements

## Production Optimizations

### Performance
- Larger batch sizes (5 vs 3)
- More concurrent requests (5 vs 3)
- Extended timeout (45s vs 30s)
- More retries (5 vs 3)
- Query caching enabled

### Reliability
- Extended retention (1 year)
- Backup management (30-day retention)
- Conflict resolution for shared use
- Comprehensive logging with rotation
- Health checks and monitoring

### Search Quality
- Both semantic and text search
- FTS (full-text search) enabled
- Lower relevance threshold (more results)
- Hybrid result ranking
- Query optimization

## Deployment Checklist

- [ ] Set appropriate retention period
- [ ] Configure team sharing if needed
- [ ] Enable encryption for sensitive data
- [ ] Set up backup destination
- [ ] Configure monitoring alerts
- [ ] Test cleanup schedule
- [ ] Verify logging rotation

## Monitoring

Production configuration includes:
- Health checks on database
- Performance tracking
- Anomaly detection
- Error alerting

## Scaling Considerations

For very large deployments (10,000+ conversations):
- Increase `max_size_mb` threshold
- Consider `max_concurrent_requests: 10`
- Enable `query_optimization: true`
- Monitor memory usage during indexing

## Backup Strategy

Production backups include:
- Automatic backups before cleanup
- 30-day backup retention
- Multiple backup rotation
- Verified backup integrity

## Security Notes

For production with sensitive data:
1. Set `encrypt_database: true`
2. Configure `access_log_enabled: true`
3. Enable `audit_trail: true`
4. Secure backup location
5. Review access permissions

## Team Usage

For team environments:
1. Configure `shared_memory: true`
2. Set `sync_enabled: true` for cloud sync
3. Define `conflict_resolution` strategy
4. Establish shared tagging conventions

## Maintenance Schedule

Weekly cleanup runs include:
- VACUUM and ANALYZE
- Old data pruning
- Index rebuilds
- Storage optimization
- Health check reporting

## Monitoring Alerts

Configure alerts for:
- Database corruption
- Indexing failures
- Disk space warnings
- Performance degradation
- Backup failures
